    • Constructor Detail

      • Tile

        public Tile​(int position,
            Picture icon)
        Constructor. Creates a new instance of the Tile class based on the starting postion and the Picture
        Parameters:
        position - the position of the particular tile stored as an int
        previousIcon - a string for what was previously at the location (to replace when the tile is moved)
        droppedNut - if the tile is a head. Stores if the head has dropped its nut already
        icon - stores a Picture of the current icon (is updated when the nut is dropped)
